title: Out With the Old, In With the O's

description:
Ready for a fresh start in 2017? In this show, Emily and Anderson are here to help you step up your game and set your own rules, both in the bedroom and in the dating world.

The two dissect the phenomena of “Sexual Black Friday” and discuss why NOW is the best time for new singles to start swiping online. They also answer your emails, from BJ’s to G-spots to the right way to date more than one person at a time.

If you’re looking for ways to make 2017 your year for better sex and romance, this podcast has what you need. Check it out…


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
